OL,3,CRoyal Marine recruit given 'thrashing'
OL,4,Con the night before he died, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA Royal Marine recruit underwent a
OL,8,F"thrashing" alongside his troop on the
OL,9,Fnight before he died, an inquest has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FConnor Clark, 18, from Norfolk, was
OL,13,Ffound dead on the railway line beside
OL,14,Fthe commando training centre in
OL,15,FLympstone, near Exeter.
OL,17,FAn inquest into his death began at the
OL,18,FExeter and Greater Devon Coroner's
OL,19,FCourt on Monday 17 June.
