OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F431A1718718648
OL,3,CRoyal Marine recruit given 'thrashing'
OL,4,Con the night before he died, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe added that it had been issued to
OL,8,Fthe entire troop over concerns of
OL,9,Ffailing to meet standards during their
OL,10,Ftraining.
OL,12,FThrashing is the term used at the
OL,13,FRoyal Marines Commando training centre
OL,14,Ffor any form of punishment or sanction.
OL,16,FDuring his own eight weeks at
OL,17,FLympstone, he said he endured around
OL,18,Ftwenty "thrashings" that mostly
OL,19,Finvolved short spells of intense
OL,20,Fexercise like press-ups.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
