OL,3,CRoyal Marine recruit given 'thrashing'
OL,4,Con the night before he died, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said he did not believe Connor was
OL,8,Ftargeted or singled out for
OL,9,Fpunishments.
OL,11,FThe pair had become friends as they
OL,12,Fwere both originally from New Zealand
OL,13,Fand got to know each other well.
OL,15,FThey were looking forward to a meal
OL,16,Fout in Exeter that weekend.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
