OL,3,CRoyal Marine recruit given 'thrashing'
OL,4,Con the night before he died, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe told the inquest that he did not
OL,8,Fsee any warning signs that Connor
OL,9,Fwanted to take his own life during the
OL,10,Ftraining, but said he would get very
OL,11,Fstressed about aspects of the course.
OL,13,FHe said Connor was struggling, not on
OL,14,Fthe physical fitness side, but with
OL,15,Ftasks relating to keeping his kit
OL,16,Forganised, ironed and well-presented
OL,17,Ffor locker inspections.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
