OL,3,CRoyal Marine recruit given 'thrashing'
OL,4,Con the night before he died, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FOn the night of 11 June he had agreed
OL,8,Fto meet Connor with others at the
OL,9,Fwashing area to help him but he did
OL,10,Fnot turn up.
OL,12,FThey could not find him and went back
OL,13,Fto their beds. He was awoken by people
OL,14,Fshouting Connor's name the following
OL,15,Fmorning.
OL,17,FChris Lee went to Connor's room. He
OL,18,Fsaw a bayonet lying on the floor and
OL,19,Fran around the block looking for him.
OL,20,FHe also found his notebook on the
OL,21,Fground floor but didn't read it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
