OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F431A1718718648
OL,3,CRoyal Marine recruit given 'thrashing'
OL,4,Con the night before he died, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FWhen he heard of his death, he said he
OL,8,Fwas completely taken by surprise and
OL,9,Fhe didn't feel like he missed any
OL,10,Fwarning signs.
OL,12,FHe told the coroner, Philip Spinney,
OL,13,Fthat he knew that Connor was stressed
OL,14,Fabout losing a piece of kit. It was a
OL,15,Fblank firing attachment that is placed
OL,16,Fon the end of rifles to indicate that
OL,17,Fit is only for firing blanks.
OL,19,FIt was said to be a piece of equipment
OL,20,Fthat could be of interest to terrorist
OL,21,Forganisations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
