OL,3,CRoyal Marine recruit given 'thrashing'
OL,4,Con the night before he died, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FChris Lee said Connor may have gotten
OL,8,Fmore stressed about the possibility of
OL,9,Flosing his right to shore leave or the
OL,10,Fnight out for losing the piece of kit.
OL,12,FThe hearing continues.
